title: B. Rides Piper
text:
My little 6 year old Grandson goes here and rides an awesome horse named Piper. The therapy he has received has been astounding, the improvement only continues to escalate. The facility, barn is something even better than you would see on a TV movie or series show. It is state of the art, which it is run off of donations. The horses are beautiful and so well trained and well cared for. The staff are the best. Check out their activities, and if you find yourself out that way, or interested in an raffle which is now on FB and other things. 
We are beyond blessed to have such a facility here is Western Ky, which provides the therapies at this level. 
May God find a way for Cassidy‚Äôs Cause to always be there to give every child who needs it a chance to improve their life, when life has given them a struggle!
